    "Notifications are turned off for 2048 Tiles in Settings, so we can't tell you when the Daily is ready.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Notifications are turned off for 2048 Tiles in Settings, so we can't tell you when the Daily is ready."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "2048 Tiles 的通知已在「設定」中關閉，因此我們無法在每日題目準備好時通知你。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "2048 Tiles 的通知已在「设置」中关闭，因此我们无法在每日题目准备好时通知你。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "2048 Tiles の通知が設定でオフになっているため、デイリーの準備ができてもお知らせできません。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "설정에서 2048 Tiles 알림이 꺼져 있어 데일리가 준비돼도 알려드릴 수 없어요."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Las notificaciones de 2048 Tiles están desactivadas en Ajustes, así que no podemos avisarte cuando el diario esté listo."
          }
        },
        "th": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "การแจ้งเตือนของ 2048 Tiles ถูกปิดในการตั้งค่า เราจึงไม่สามารถบอกคุณได้เมื่อโจทย์ประจำวันพร้อม"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "#479 SDD-005 — notifications denied message for 2048 Tiles."
    },
